<template>
  <v-row>
    <v-col
      md="3"
      sm="6">
      <v-expansion-panels inset>
        <v-expansion-panel
          v-for="(plan,i) in plans"
          :key="i"
          flat
          tile>
          <v-expansion-panel-header>{{ plan.name }}</v-expansion-panel-header>
          <v-expansion-panel-content>
            {{ plan.description}}
          </v-expansion-panel-content>
        </v-expansion-panel>
      </v-expansion-panels>
    </v-col>
  </v-row>
</template>
